      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，PLC逻辑作为数据源，边缘节点做本地处理。那它们之间的数据流关系是？是PLC直接把原始数据推给边缘节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，PLC逻辑产生的数据要先经过边缘节点的Chunk & Process处理，这是第一步1a。边缘节点负责分块和预处理，减轻云端压力。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "1a. Chunk & Process"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Knowledge_Base子图已经画好，包含D节点PLC逻辑指向C节点边缘节点，标注1a。接下来知识库的输出流向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "1a. Chunk & Process"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "处理后的数据要生成向量嵌入，流向IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker，这是步骤1b Generate Embeddings。MQTT Broker在这里充当向量数据库的入口。",
      "elements_involved": [
