      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我注意到后面还有个IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker节点，和这里的DB是同一个组件吗？还是不同的实例？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
